x = 4 
f'(x) = 12 x^2 - 5 + \frac{1}{\sqrt{x} } 
 \therefore f'(4) = 12(4)^2 - 5 + \frac{1}{\sqrt{4}} = 192 - 5 + \frac{1}{2} = 187 + \frac{1}{2} = 187.5 
